title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Addon spotlight - Mosquito XE Helicopter Project - version 02b
description:
In this video we are going to look at the Mosquito XE Helicopter which is a single seater helicopter which is still under development. Even though it is still under development you can already fly around with it perfectly fine.
After looking at the outside we will review the inside, start the engines and take it out for a short flight

If you would like to try Mosquito XE Helicopter Project yourself download it from the site below:
https://flightsim.to/file/29050/mosquito-xe-helicopter-project-wip
